snippet.title: Within the Backrooms - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Within the Backrooms Official Trailer

Release Date: January 13th, 2023

Within the Backrooms is a liminal exploration game with light puzzle elements. Use tools you find and mysterious floppy disks to traverse the world, uncover the secrets of the Backrooms, and find out why you're here. 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2158740/Within_the_Backrooms/

Music Composed by eze
